1.3.39.name: wordpress/export-readers
1.3.39.description:
This plugin is only supported on PHP 5.2 or greater.

ExportReaders easily allows you to export your users details for use elsewhere. Just select the roles you with to export and set the criteria to select the commenters and download its that simple.

If you are having trouble and cannot find the answers in the FAQ you can post your support questions to the WordPress Support Forum

If you find ExportReaders useful please rate it at wordpress.org and please consider making a donation to help us set aside more hours to maintain ExportReaders

ExportReaders is written by dcoda

You can check out our other plugins
